data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY SEPT 3  1PM  TO 3PM Well, maintained 4 bedroom 2 bath two living in older neighborhood in the fastest growing community in central Texas. Gardener's delight. Back yard loaded with plants with a nice sitting area. Small garden area on the side of the house. Mother-in-law plan. Several painted accent walls throughout the home. Granite counter tops with tile backsplash. Easy access to highway 79. Short drive to Taylor, Round Rock and Pflugerville. Centrally located to the new Samsung in Taylor and Amazon in Pflugerville and the Telsa giga factory on 130.
